    ## Projects
    
    ### Lotus Notes to PEGA Transformation
    Transformation of Lotus Notes applications to PEGA Case Management. Harnessed the power of PEGA to create a seamless and efficient customer experience for different business lines like Asset Servicing, Settlements, Corporate actions and Tax.
    *Technologies used: PEGA Architecture, PEGA Case Management, PEGA Constellation, PEGA Cloud, Theme Cosmos, Java, REST API*
    
    ### Monitor Alert
    Automated alert generation for Business lending. Monitor Alert is an alert monitoring tool in risk area in Banking. Based on the non-payment of the loans by the end customers due various reasons alerts are generated by external system and passed on to PEGA for case creation and case handling to make a decision about customer.
    *Technologies used: PEGA Case Management, File integration, BIX extract, REST API*
